Introduction

Seo Ji Soo is the former main dancer and vocalist of the girl group Lovelyz under Woollim Entertainment.

She debuted as a member of Lovelyz with their first studio album Girls' Invasion on November 17, 2014.

On November 1, 2021, Woollim Entertainment announced 7 of the members, except Baby Soul, had chosen not to renew their contracts which expired on November 16.

On January 4, 2022, she announced that she has signed an exclusive contract with MYSTIC Story to promote as an actress.
